===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-pizzicato.ogg|Audio (US)}} 

===Adverb===
'''pizzicato'''
#{{music}} An instruction to players of [[stringed]] [[instrument]]s to [[pluck]] the strings instead of using the [[bow]].  Abbreviation: pizz.

